<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/741011-would-you-categorise-this-book-as-a">Would you categorise this book as a general YA book like Divergent and the Hunger Games? With the generic female protagonist that saves the government and has one of those terrible &#39;love-triangles&#39;? I&#39;m planning to go on a major trip to the bookstore soon, and I want to know whether it will make it on my list</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_741011'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F407813.The_Blue_Sword">like</a></span>

</li>
